name: FChaosPhysicsSettings
doc:
Settings container for Chaos physics engine settings, accessed in Chaos through a setting provider interface.
See: IChaosSettingsProvider

DefaultThreadingModel: Default threading model to use on module initialisation. Can be switched at runtime using p.Chaos.ThreadingModel
DedicatedThreadTickMode: The framerate/timestep ticking mode when running with a dedicated thread
DedicatedThreadBufferMode: The buffering mode to use when running with a dedicated thread
